|3 |  │ └─HASH RIGHT SEMI JOIN |    |3       |6           |
|4 |  │   ├─TABLE FULL SCAN    |t3  |3       |3           |
|5 |  │   └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |t1  |5       |3           |
|6 |  └─TABLE FULL SCAN        |t2  |1       |3           |
===========================================================
